      <div type="inscription" xml:lang="en" decls="#f_W #c_2 #m_I #t_P">
        <ab rend="Alignl">+OVER THE GRAVE OF ALFRED GATLEY SCULPTOR IN ROME WHO DIED ON THE</ab>
        <ab rend="Alignl">28 JUNE 1863 HE WAS GREAT IN HIS WORKS A LOYAL CITIZEN BELOVED BY MANY</ab>
        <ab rend="Alignl">RESPECTED BY ALL HE HAD KINDNESS OF HEART A HATRED OF ALL THAT WAS</ab>
        <ab rend="Alignl">FALSE HE LIVED A CHRISTIAN'S LIFE AND DIED AT THE AGE OF 40 YEARS.</ab>
      </div>
      <div type="inscription" xml:lang="it" decls="#f_E #c_2 #m_I #t_P">
        <ab rend="Alignl">+SULLA TOMBA DI ALFEDO GATLEY SCULTORE IN ROMA. MORTO LI 28 GIUGNO</ab>
        <ab rend="Alignl">1863 EGLI FU GRANDE NELLE SUE OPERE D'ARTE CITTADINO LEALE AMATO DA</ab>
        <ab rend="Alignl">MOLTI RISPETTATO DA TUTTI EBBE GRAN BONTÀ DI CUORE ED ODIO DEL FALSO</ab>
        <ab rend="Alignl">VISSE CRISTIANAMENTE E MORÌ ALL ETA DI ANNI 40.</ab>
      </div>
    </body>
